{"tid":434341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國懸崖邊拍「橫空出世」跳躍　韓女墜崖慘死","createTime":"2017-10-13T08:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T18:46:35.000Z","uid":75969,"like":191,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":120,"replies":[{"pid":"a19f0320cd0f0427cc8f1b406deddb1298327c18","tid":434341,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T08:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171013/420_a3b1e0416c7b2470de9ed56c37ff8569.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171013%2F420_a3b1e0416c7b2470de9ed56c37ff8569.jpg&h=e72c75cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">不少目擊者指出，幫金惠媛拍照時，她騰空跳躍，卻失足墜崖。翻自《每日郵報》<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n南韓一名23歲女子金惠媛(Hyewon Kim，譯音)，在今年6月前往英國東薩塞克斯郡(East Sussex)著名觀光景點「七姐妹崖」拍照留念，她為了製造「橫空出世」的效果，在懸崖邊騰空跳躍，卻沒想到一個失足跌落懸崖，最後不幸身亡。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，金惠媛是前往英國學習英文的南韓女學生，當時她到觀光景點「七姐妹崖」拍照留念，並拜託旁邊其他旅客為她拍照。一名24歲同樣來自南韓的目擊者崔英(Young Choi，譯音)表示，當時金惠媛拜託他幫忙拍攝，「在我拍照的時候，她就掉下懸崖了，我趕快報警和尋求南韓大使館的協助」。<br />\n<br />\n消防員哈里森(Richard Harrison)指出，他獲報後趕到現場，發現金惠媛墜落約60公尺深的懸崖，並發現她臉部朝下倒地。<br />\n<br />\n之後金惠媛的驗屍報告出爐，表示金惠媛頭部重創，是其致命傷。而在她的手機裡，也發現6張當時在「七姐妹崖」邊拍攝的照片。台灣網友紛紛表示：「變八姐妹崖。」、「橫空出事。」、「不見棺材不掉淚，轉眼已在甕裡面。」、「這下真的無腦。」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171013/420_558b6b559a0d19a85aa8af1e76d1f10c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171013%2F420_558b6b559a0d19a85aa8af1e76d1f10c.jpg&h=7f2012e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171013/1221568/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20171013%2F1221568%2F&d=0djIjg1J8pqMBubz4BkWbf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=72dfe07d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171013/1221568/</a>"},{"pid":"ba8b00c83b6998b08c3a02dcde58a4aa290284a4","tid":434341,"uid":75969,"like":320,"dislike":2,"score":318,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T08:02:56.000Z","msg":"變咗「橫空離世，投胎出世」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6051823f3c1b9ad30b28a699c5c489aef15478f","tid":434341,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T08:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7076bb4eb4993521f3a57492eb5cc84323ec8b9","tid":434341,"uid":8016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T08:03:14.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"ed6f6f6b0e77f6e841fae8153222619956b968fd","tid":434341,"uid":39628,"like":385,"dislike":0,"score":385,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T08:03:53.000Z","msg":"變八姐妹崖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1dd6f69246de05f3890eba1c19d2582d0e13148","tid":434341,"uid":6845,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T08:04:16.000Z","msg":"41J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6073d04af635bc76aaa25d0895c7dca8d7186ee","tid":434341,"uid":52819,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T08:06:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>變八姐妹崖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f62d06b26249e237af822a6e4f50caae161c62","tid":434341,"uid":125061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T08:09:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>變八姐妹崖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf655973b7565ad52